ComicInfo.Summary:
Sensitive Klegg returns! Yes, it’s another pulse-pounding issue of the legendary British weekly comic, including: Judge Dredd: Ghosts by Rob Williams, D’Israeli, and Annie Parkhouse; Strontium Dog: Repo Men by John Wagner, Carlos Ezquerra, Simon Bowland; The Order: In the Court of the WyrmQueene by Kek-W, John Burns, Ellie De Ville; ABC Warriors: Return to Ro-Busters by Pat Mills, Clint Langley, Annie Parkhouse; and Kingdom: Beast of Eden by Dan Abnett, Richard Elson, Ellie De Ville.
Cover: Alex Ronald
